I"ä`<h2 id="the-computer">The Computer</h2>

<ul>
  <li>a computer system is made up of various elements</li>
  <li>each of these elements affects the interaction
    <ul>
      <li>input devices ‚Äì text entry and pointing</li>
      <li>output devices ‚Äì screen (small&amp;large), digital paper</li>
      <li>virtual reality ‚Äì special interaction and display devices</li>
      <li>physical interaction ‚Äì e.g. sound, haptic, bio-sensing</li>
      <li>paper ‚Äì as output (print) and input (scan)</li>
      <li>memory ‚Äì RAM &amp; permanent media, capacity &amp; access</li>
      <li>processing ‚Äì speed of processing, networks</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

