<h2 id="a-typical-computer-system">A ‚Äòtypical‚Äô computer system</h2>

<ul>
  <li>screen, or monitor, on which there are windows</li>
  <li>keyboard</li>
  <li>
    <p>mouse/trackpad <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/speardragon/save-image-repo/main/img/image-20220919121321481.png" alt="image-20220919121321481" /></p>
  </li>
  <li>variations
    <ul>
      <li>desktop</li>
      <li>laptop</li>
      <li>tablet</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>the devices dictate(Íµ¨Ïà†ÌïòÎã§) the styles of interaction that the system supports</li>
  <li>If we use different devices, then the interface will support a different style of interaction</li>
</ul>

