<h2 id="virtual-reality-and-3d-interaction-3d-displays">Virtual reality and 3D interaction: 3D displays</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Desktop VR
    <ul>
      <li>Ordinary screen, mouse or keyboard control</li>
      <li>Perspective and motion give 3D effect</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Seeing in 3D
    <ul>
      <li>Use stereoscopic vision</li>
      <li>VR helmets</li>
      <li>Screen plus shuttered specs, etc</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/speardragon/save-image-repo/main/img/image-20220909222750595.png" alt="image-20220909222750595" /></p>

