<h2 id="vr-motion-sickness">VR motion sickness</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Time delay
    <ul>
      <li>move head ‚Ä¶ lag ‚Ä¶ display moves</li>
      <li>conflict: head movement vs. eyes</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Depth perception
    <ul>
      <li>headset gives different stereo distance</li>
      <li>but all focused in same plane</li>
      <li>conflict: eye angle vs. focus</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Conflicting cues =&gt; sickness
    <ul>
      <li>helps motivate improvements in technology</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

