    <ul>
      <li>dials, gauges, lights, etc.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Digital displays:
    <ul>
      <li>small LCD screens, LED lights, etc.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Head-up displays (HUD)
    <ul>
      <li>found in aircraft cockpits(ÏΩïÏΩï) or automobiles</li>
      <li>show most important controls ‚Ä¶ depending on context</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Hologram
    <ul>
      <li>Gatebox animated robot</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
